{"tid":1419814,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"連登分化","createTime":"2019-08-06T02:42:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T08:57:54.000Z","uid":286412,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"17e9705e21d0793e87e3f26f019609785962e4bb","tid":1419814,"uid":286412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T02:42:13.000Z","msg":"我今朝一起身就見到好多post係連登仔互鬧大家，互相批判責罵大家，如果咁樣做你哋覺得可以贏請你地繼續，如果唔係我哋就係正中敵人嘅圈套，我哋自己越亂人就越開心，大家記住連登係呢場運動嘅根，如果個根爛咗，棵樹就會爛啲花就會謝到時點樣都唔使我再講。總言之一定要停止分化同停止內亂，大家要記住個敵人係邊個，同五個目標。"},{"pid":"50e04094f052b512772b5e5204ef694d2b1685c2","tid":1419814,"uid":286412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T02:44:23.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"7524e0a5b999169280cb90871e8b315ae7aaf8bb","tid":1419814,"uid":286412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T03:10:33.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"9f6ce089ccedfac5e3ab8de147a476156f8c7d72","tid":1419814,"uid":286412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T03:14:06.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"8a8cafe34ca1c87502a2356f9a9308e5f0cd0a1b","tid":1419814,"uid":286412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T03:14:44.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"6dbd1a14a140f54ba8d850c0bc80f38a6d82de60","tid":1419814,"uid":286412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T03:25:39.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"59a1b5e3c5b406c3789e42bd4dfb574ab00a941e","tid":1419814,"uid":286412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T05:11:28.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"18e37543dea1a32e21ba2a20886b1ef60ebfd366","tid":1419814,"uid":286412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T05:39:55.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"e9a317acca4d55eac8ce68d74a69ffe9f742a5d2","tid":1419814,"uid":286412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T05:57:19.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"c5072f88b430149d89ea3293d9f24db2634ba839","tid":1419814,"uid":286412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"s